QuestData.Title: Aspirant Elynna
QuestData.Description:
$n! You've returned to the Maw! Glory be with you!
I have news. It seems that one of the aspirants lost in the attack on Honorveil is being held here, in the Jailor's Armory. Her name is Elynna, and she's on the tenth floor.
That's all I know for now. We shall speak again when I know more.
QuestData.LogDescription: Find Aspirant Elynna on the tenth floor of the Jailer's Tower.

Objectives.Objective: Find Elynna deeper in the Maw
